{"synckey":1728434042,"updated":[{"bookId":"3300115299","bookmarkId":"3300115299_8_698-746","createTime":1728434042,"chapterUid":8,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"为什么这样的人虽认为自己有逻辑，但别人却不认同呢？这是因为他说话的论据时常出现跳跃，语言不连贯。","range":"698-746"},{"bookId":"3300115299","bookmarkId":"3300115299_8_588-623","createTime":1728434032,"chapterUid":8,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"所谓有逻辑，就是要建立逻辑结构，从而得出结论，使结论的正当性有理可循。","range":"588-623"},{"bookId":"3300115299","bookmarkId":"3300115299_7_1880-1925","createTime":1728433873,"chapterUid":7,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"一定要首先思考“目的是什么”，这是最重要的问题。把“究竟为了什么”清晰化，以此作为出发点。","range":"1880-1925"},{"bookId":"3300115299","bookmarkId":"3300115299_7_1312-1681","createTime":1728433780,"chapterUid":7,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"对资料进行整理并分析首先试着将目的明确化[插图]主动思考，使自己的想法明确化将备选方案排序并对其进行分析","range":"1312-1681"},{"bookId":"3300115299","bookmarkId":"3300115299_7_595-630","createTime":1728391792,"chapterUid":7,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"如果大脑中总是一片混乱，各种想法得不到整理，那么就不可能进行逻辑思考。","range":"595-630"},{"bookId":"3300115299","bookmarkId":"3300115299_7_568-595","createTime":1728391783,"chapterUid":7,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"所谓逻辑思考力就是建立逻辑思维来对问题进行分析的能力。","range":"568-595"},{"bookId":"3300115299","bookmarkId":"3300115299_4_1511-1535","createTime":1728391653,"chapterUid":4,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"有时会被说“说话思维不连贯”或“说话总是省略”。","range":"1511-1535"}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"跳跃式思考，不能让对方明白想表达的意思","chapterUid":8,"chapterIdx":8},{"title":"逻辑思考力使人进步","chapterUid":7,"chapterIdx":7},{"title":"逻辑思考力小测试","chapterUid":4,"chapterIdx":4}],"book":{"bookId":"3300115299","version":57049413,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/48/cpplatform_8hkqj76vppwjhtzozuime8/s_cpplatform_8hkqj76vppwjhtzozuime81726729542.jpg","title":"逻辑思考力：脑子真的会变快！","author":"西村克己","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KDSiaBW=_NIuW=sk%fbHMx","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#370f06"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#3f0600"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#